My build of DWM.

includes the gaplessgrid, stacker, status2d and tilewide patches (maybe more but I don't think so).
uses the 'CaskaydiaCove Nerd Font', which can be downloaded here: https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/releases/download/v2.3.3/CascadiaCode.zip
has the windows-key set as the modkey and has keys set for adjusting volume and brightness (if you have those)
